@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_xsglkm(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = (wp.sin((tmp + 0.24 * tmp + 0.23)) + 0.96)
    tmp = (tmp - ((tmp + 0.97 * v0 + 0.29) / wp.exp(v1 + 0.89)))
    v1 = v2
    v2 = wp.exp(0.94)
    tmp = 0.89
    v2 = (tmp - (wp.cos(v0 + 0.45) * 0.77))
    v1 = ((wp.abs(v1 + 0.32) + (v2 + 0.04 - tmp + 0.58)) / ((v1 + 0.04 + v1 + 0.26) + 0.76))
    data[tid] = v0
